= SDL_WaitThread =
Use this function to wait for a thread to finish.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_WaitThread(SDL_Thread* thread,
                    int*        status)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''thread'''
|^a pointer to the [[SDL_Thread]]() to wait for^
|-
|'''status'''
|^a pointer filled with status data^; see [[#Remarks|Remarks]] for details
|}

